data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Motivated Seller! Well-maintained POOL Home with an outstanding view, no rear neighbors. NO CDD, Low HOA. This absolutely beautiful 4 Bedrooms, 3 Bathrooms home has it all. Entering this home, you will be delighted with the high ceilings, formal living and formal dining room area, plus spacious family room to entertain your family and friends. Renovated kitchen with newly stainless-steel appliances, bar seating area and dinette area to enjoy morning breakfast. The salted water/heated Pool with Jacuzzi in the oversized screened lanai is the perfect spot to watch the sunset or to enjoy the Floridian lifestyle. A/C is 2 years old. This house is ready to be called home, schedule your showing today before this GEM is gone.
